      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's like there's this one specific brand of politics that everyone is forced to accept, and if you question it, you're labeled as something terrible. i feel like the \"awareness\" part is just an excuse to label any disagreement as hate or something. at what point do we stop calling it \"social justice\" and just admit it's actually about controlling what people are allowed to say and think?",
